00:10:07.565 --> 00:10:09.275 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Or maybe it's the other
way around.

147
00:10:09.359 --> 00:10:11.402 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
What are you--? Get outta
my way!

148
00:10:11.528 --> 00:10:13.822 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Look, maybe it's not the kid
that needs saving.

149
00:10:13.947 --> 00:10:15.198 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You see where I'm going
with this?

150
00:10:15.281 --> 00:10:16.324 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
No!

151
00:10:16.407 --> 00:10:18.535 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
What if he's the NEXT
controlling the statue?

152
00:10:18.618 --> 00:10:20.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Well, he's still
in danger!

153
00:10:20.245 --> 00:10:22.122 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Maybe the kid's a NEXT
with telekinetic powers!

154
00:10:22.247 --> 00:10:24.999 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Well, while you're thinkin'
about it, I'm goin' in!

155
00:10:26.334 --> 00:10:29.129 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I wouldn't be so hasty.
Remember what happened last time.

156
00:10:29.212 --> 00:10:31.256 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Hey, that was
an accident.

157
00:10:31.422 --> 00:10:34.050 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You know? I'm beginning
to seriously question your judgement.

158
00:10:35.301 --> 00:10:36.594 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I never liked
this idea.

159
00:10:37.095 --> 00:10:40.765 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
If the sponsors weren't insisting on it,
I'd quit this team right now.

160
00:10:41.641 --> 00:10:43.017 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
That makes two of us.

161
00:10:45.854 --> 00:10:46.729 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
Uh-oh...

162
00:10:50.233 --> 00:10:51.151 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
[screaming]

163
00:10:51.526 --> 00:10:53.153 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
Don't move or
you're all dead!

164
00:10:54.737 --> 00:10:56.364 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[panicking]
Don't hurt us!

165
00:11:05.915 --> 00:11:06.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
You!

166
00:11:06.958 --> 00:11:08.376 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Drop the gun.

167
00:11:08.459 --> 00:11:10.378 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Why, it's Mr. Legend.

168
00:11:11.671 --> 00:11:13.923 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[screaming]

169
00:11:17.260 --> 00:11:18.386 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[grunting]

170
00:11:18.469 --> 00:11:19.804 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Oh, wow!

171
00:11:20.513 --> 00:11:22.015 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Huh!

172
00:11:22.098 --> 00:11:23.433 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[groaning]

173
00:11:23.516 --> 00:11:25.226 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[panicking]

174
00:11:25.768 --> 00:11:27.478 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
One more move and
the kid gets it!

175
00:11:27.562 --> 00:11:28.479 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Huh?

176
00:11:34.319 --> 00:11:35.195 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[screaming]

177
00:11:35.403 --> 00:11:36.738 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
What the hell's wrong
with this kid?!

178
00:11:40.742 --> 00:11:41.993 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
What do you know.

179
00:11:43.494 --> 00:11:44.495 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Keep away.

180
00:11:44.662 --> 00:11:45.538 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Huh?

181
00:11:46.456 --> 00:11:49.792 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You don't want to come anywhere near me
when I start to glow like this.

182
00:11:49.876 --> 00:11:51.127 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
And why's that?

183
00:11:52.045 --> 00:11:54.797 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Because... I hurt people.

184
00:11:54.923 --> 00:11:56.507 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
You've got it wrong.

185
00:11:57.091 --> 00:12:00.261 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
With those powers of yours,
you can save people.

186
00:12:06.893 --> 00:12:10.897 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
After all, you saved me.
That makes you a hero, too.

187
00:12:14.400 --> 00:12:15.276 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[giggling]

188
00:12:27.789 --> 00:12:29.207 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Have a nice nap,
old man?

189
00:12:29.624 --> 00:12:32.126 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Funny. You gonna tell
me what happened?

190
00:12:32.210 --> 00:12:34.629 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
The statue grabbed us,
and then he stopped again.

191
00:12:34.712 --> 00:12:37.173 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
And you're just sittin'
here? Why don't you escape?

192
00:12:37.465 --> 00:12:38.466 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Well, I can't!

193
00:12:38.549 --> 00:12:39.509 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Huh?

194
00:12:39.634 --> 00:12:41.135 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Without using my power, I mean.

195
00:12:41.219 --> 00:12:43.721 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Then use it, you idiot!
What're you waiting for?!

196
00:12:43.846 --> 00:12:47.308 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
We've only got five minutes.
I want to save it 'til I really need it.

197
00:12:47.934 --> 00:12:52.230 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Unbelievable. Well, suit yourself,
little bunny, I'm out of here!

198
00:12:52.397 --> 00:12:53.273 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Whoa, whoa, hold it!

199
00:12:53.398 --> 00:12:54.774 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
What?!

200
00:12:54.857 --> 00:12:58.403 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
What did you call me?
Did you just call me Bunny?!

201
00:12:58.528 --> 00:13:00.780 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Yeah, why not? You've got
those long, pink ears

202
00:13:00.863 --> 00:13:02.365 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
and you're always hoppin' around.

203
00:13:02.448 --> 00:13:04.242 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You're just like a
cute little bunny--

204
00:13:04.325 --> 00:13:06.953 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I am not a bunny!
My name is Barnaby!

205
00:13:07.453 --> 00:13:09.664 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I am not a bunny,
I'm a Barnaby!

206
00:13:09.747 --> 00:13:10.707 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I don't talk like that!

207
00:13:11.291 --> 00:13:12.959 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I don't talk
like that!

208
00:13:13.167 --> 00:13:14.294 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-[Agnes] <i>Heads up, you two.</i>
-Huh?

209
00:13:14.460 --> 00:13:16.629 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
We've got another statue going
on a rampage.

210
00:13:17.088 --> 00:13:20.091 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[Agnes] <i>There's a giant stone lion headed</i>
<i>toward the New Morghen district.</i>

211
00:13:20.591 --> 00:13:22.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[Kotetsu] <i>What?! That's where</i>
<i>the ice rink is!</i>

212
00:13:24.595 --> 00:13:29.309 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[grunting]

213
00:13:31.394 --> 00:13:32.895 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
You mind getting me out, too?

214
00:13:33.855 --> 00:13:34.856 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Huh?

215
00:13:35.023 --> 00:13:38.609 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Well. I mean. You're all powered-up
and everything...

216
00:13:39.319 --> 00:13:41.154 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
You're right, I am.

217
00:13:48.453 --> 00:13:52.790 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[phone ringing]

218
00:13:57.545 --> 00:14:00.089 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[laughing]

219
00:14:01.257 --> 00:14:03.343 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Come on, Isaac,
we've gotta get ready.

220
00:14:06.554 --> 00:14:10.516 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[woman announcer] <i>All participants, please</i>
<i>assemble backstage now.</i>

221
00:14:21.569 --> 00:14:23.529 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Daddy's coming,
Kaede!

222
00:14:27.700 --> 00:14:28.701 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Gotcha!

223
00:14:28.785 --> 00:14:29.786 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Agnes] <i>Tiger, you read me?</i>

224
00:14:29.911 --> 00:14:30.912 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yeah!

225
00:14:30.995 --> 00:14:32.872 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-[Agnes] <i>You can't use your wire guns!</i>
-What?

226
00:14:32.997 --> 00:14:37.585 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
The statue's a historic cultural artifact.
The Government doesn't want it damaged.

227
00:14:38.586 --> 00:14:42.340 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Well tell them too bad! Saving the lives
of innocent people comes first!

228
00:14:43.007 --> 00:14:45.259 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Agnes] <i>You break it, you buy it!</i>

229
00:14:46.094 --> 00:14:47.095 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Meaning?

230
00:14:47.595 --> 00:14:51.432 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
The statue's a national treasure.
You have any idea how much it's worth?

231
00:14:52.183 --> 00:14:54.352 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Oh, Got it.

232
00:14:59.023 --> 00:15:02.610 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Hey! Kid!
Come on down from there.

233
00:15:03.736 --> 00:15:05.279 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Stay away!

234
00:15:05.405 --> 00:15:07.782 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[roaring]

235
00:15:09.117 --> 00:15:10.201 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Wait--!

236
00:15:11.536 --> 00:15:12.703 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Huh?

237
00:15:17.917 --> 00:15:19.001 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Oh, no!

238
00:15:20.545 --> 00:15:21.629 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[grunting]

239
00:15:25.675 --> 00:15:27.093 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[screaming]

240
00:15:31.055 --> 00:15:32.765 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[roaring]

241
00:15:32.932 --> 00:15:37.854 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[panicking]

242
00:15:41.441 --> 00:15:43.568 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Oh, no.
I can't stop it!

243
00:15:48.406 --> 00:15:51.367 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[grunting]

244
00:15:51.659 --> 00:15:52.869 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
This way, folks!

245
00:15:58.166 --> 00:15:59.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Kaede--!

246
00:16:06.507 --> 00:16:10.970 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
No!

247
00:16:26.694 --> 00:16:28.029 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Kaede...

248
00:16:31.532 --> 00:16:33.534 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Thank you so much, mister.

249
00:16:33.659 --> 00:16:35.036 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[gasping]
Huh?!

250
00:16:37.788 --> 00:16:39.332 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Now you get
on out of here.

251
00:16:39.415 --> 00:16:40.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I sure will.

252
00:16:43.920 --> 00:16:47.465 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Hey, um...
thanks.

253
00:16:49.592 --> 00:16:52.011 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Thanks for what?
I didn't save your life, did I?

254
00:16:52.094 --> 00:16:53.304 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
No, but--

255
00:16:53.387 --> 00:16:56.516 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Help me! Help!
[screaming]

256
00:17:02.021 --> 00:17:03.814 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Stay out of my way.

257
00:17:04.273 --> 00:17:06.192 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Why are you
doing this, kid?!

258
00:17:06.275 --> 00:17:08.486 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
He knows why!
He and the others!

259
00:17:08.569 --> 00:17:09.612 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
What do you mean?

260
00:17:09.737 --> 00:17:13.824 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
My whole life they've hated me and
treated me like I was some kind of freak!

261
00:17:15.034 --> 00:17:18.371 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
No, not your whole life, just since
you started to make things move!

262
00:17:20.248 --> 00:17:24.043 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Normal kids can't do what you do.
I mean, it freaks us out.

263
00:17:24.168 --> 00:17:26.170 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
We don't hate you,
we're scared of you!

264
00:17:26.254 --> 00:17:29.257 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I didn't ask to be given
these powers! It's not my fault!

265
00:17:29.423 --> 00:17:31.759 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
We don't want you
around! Just go away!

266
00:17:33.094 --> 00:17:34.470 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
You're going away.

267
00:17:34.971 --> 00:17:36.931 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[roaring]

268
00:17:38.474 --> 00:17:41.477 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Slow down, kid. I know
just how you feel.

269
00:17:41.686 --> 00:17:42.812 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
No, you don't!

270
00:17:42.937 --> 00:17:45.773 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I do... because it happened to me, too.

271
00:17:45.856 --> 00:17:48.484 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I was about your age when
I found out I was a NEXT.

272
00:17:48.651 --> 00:17:49.610 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Huh?

273
00:17:52.738 --> 00:17:55.658 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
My friends turned on me,
called me a freak...

274
00:17:55.741 --> 00:17:56.993 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I hated them for that.

275
00:17:57.910 --> 00:18:00.705 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Most of all,
I hated my powers.

276
00:18:00.871 --> 00:18:02.915 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Then a hero called
Mr. Legend came along

277
00:18:03.082 --> 00:18:05.585 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
and told me something
that changed my life.

278
00:18:06.836 --> 00:18:09.714 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
With those powers of yours,
you can save people.

279
00:18:11.465 --> 00:18:12.550 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
My powers can't.

280
00:18:12.967 --> 00:18:14.176 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Why not?

281
00:18:14.302 --> 00:18:18.180 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Because they're not like a real hero's
powers, all I can do is make stuff move.

282
00:18:18.306 --> 00:18:21.475 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Trust me, one day you will
find the right use for them.

283
00:18:21.601 --> 00:18:22.560 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I promise.

284
00:18:22.643 --> 00:18:23.811 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
You mean it?

285
00:18:23.936 --> 00:18:25.563 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You could be
one of the best.

286
00:18:25.646 --> 00:18:26.856 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Really?!

287
00:18:26.939 --> 00:18:28.816 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sure. Now come on down

288
00:18:28.899 --> 00:18:30.985 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
and let's have the police
call your parents.

289
00:18:31.193 --> 00:18:32.361 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
What are you doing?

290
00:18:32.486 --> 00:18:34.530 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
If we don't arrest him,
we don't score any points.

291
00:18:34.614 --> 00:18:36.324 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Oh, shut up!
Will ya?!

292
00:18:37.074 --> 00:18:39.285 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Okay, kid, you wanna be a hero,

293
00:18:39.410 --> 00:18:42.705 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
this is the first step. What do ya say?
You gonna come down?

294
00:18:52.048 --> 00:18:53.966 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
It's gonna be
okay, Tony.

295
00:18:59.055 --> 00:19:00.306 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Mm!

296
00:19:02.975 --> 00:19:04.060 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Are you okay?

297
00:19:04.143 --> 00:19:05.686 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Watch out!
The building's collapsing!

298
00:19:09.065 --> 00:19:10.316 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I'm on it!

299
00:19:13.444 --> 00:19:14.570 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Let's go!

300
00:19:15.237 --> 00:19:17.073 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[screams]

301
00:19:19.158 --> 00:19:20.326 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Help me! Somebody!

302
00:19:20.785 --> 00:19:23.329 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I got it.
Save your power.

303
00:19:26.165 --> 00:19:28.292 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Damn! We're losin' it!

304
00:19:29.460 --> 00:19:31.170 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Glad to see you, buddy!

305
00:19:31.253 --> 00:19:32.672 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Thanks and thanks again!

306
00:19:32.797 --> 00:19:33.673 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Uh-oh...

307
00:19:33.798 --> 00:19:35.299 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
What's wrong, Tiger?

308
00:19:35.383 --> 00:19:36.258 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I'm outta time.

309
00:19:36.342 --> 00:19:37.218 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Huh?

310
00:19:37.301 --> 00:19:38.344 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Power's about to run out!

311
00:19:38.427 --> 00:19:40.638 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Well, we gotta do something!

312
00:19:40.763 --> 00:19:41.847 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hey, Tony!

313
00:19:41.972 --> 00:19:44.392 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
We can't hold it, it's gonna fall!

314
00:19:44.558 --> 00:19:46.352 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[screaming]

315
00:19:46.519 --> 00:19:49.897 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
We need your help, Tony!
We need you now!

316
00:19:50.356 --> 00:19:51.565 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I can't--

317
00:19:51.649 --> 00:19:54.151 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
You can do it! I know you can!

318
00:19:55.277 --> 00:19:59.949 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I'm down to five seconds!...
Four... three... two!

319
00:20:01.033 --> 00:20:05.788 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[grunting]

320
00:20:07.581 --> 00:20:08.874 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[gasping]

321
00:20:19.969 --> 00:20:21.178 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[giggling]

322
00:20:21.470 --> 00:20:27.309 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[cheering]

323
00:20:30.896 --> 00:20:33.566 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Unless I'm mistaken,
you just saved the day, Tony.

324
00:20:33.649 --> 00:20:37.027 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Do you know what that means?
Means you're a hero.

325
00:20:37.111 --> 00:20:38.320 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I'm a hero?

326
00:20:45.411 --> 00:20:49.415 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[siren wailing]

327
00:20:52.668 --> 00:20:54.295 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hey, Tony!

328
00:20:56.797 --> 00:20:58.549 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
You were awesome back there.

329
00:20:58.883 --> 00:21:00.009 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Oh!

330
00:21:00.259 --> 00:21:01.761 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[chuckling]

331
00:21:07.892 --> 00:21:10.561 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Come on, you have
plenty of power left.

332
00:21:10.644 --> 00:21:14.565 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Huh? Whoa, well, what
do you know about that?

333
00:21:17.818 --> 00:21:19.445 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
The guy's a loose cannon,

334
00:21:19.570 --> 00:21:21.489 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I don't think this team
thing is gonna work.

335
00:21:22.323 --> 00:21:24.575 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
On the contrary,
it's working perfectly.

336
00:21:24.658 --> 00:21:25.659 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yes, but I--

337
00:21:25.785 --> 00:21:28.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
The two of you have captured
people's attention.

338
00:21:28.245 --> 00:21:30.414 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Viewership is up whenever you're on.

339
00:21:30.623 --> 00:21:32.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Now's your chance to
sell yourself.

340
00:21:32.875 --> 00:21:36.420 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
There's a reason you revealed
your true identity to the public.

341
00:21:36.796 --> 00:21:39.924 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You're not going to let all your
careful preparations go to waste,

342
00:21:40.049 --> 00:21:41.342 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
are you, my boy?

343
00:21:41.717 --> 00:21:42.802 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
No, sir.

344
00:21:43.928 --> 00:21:45.638 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Kotetsu] I'm just glad you're all right.

345
00:21:45.805 --> 00:21:48.390 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Kaede] <i>I'm fine, but it was so scary!</i>

346
00:21:49.016 --> 00:21:52.061 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I'm sorry, honey.
I should've been there to protect you.

347
00:21:52.144 --> 00:21:54.063 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
That's what a dad's for, right?

348
00:21:54.188 --> 00:21:56.565 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[Kaede] <i>Oh, I had plenty of</i>
<i>protection, Dad.</i>

349
00:21:56.649 --> 00:21:57.525 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Huh?

350
00:21:57.608 --> 00:22:00.820 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[Kaede] <i>This guy Barnaby saved me.</i>
<i>He's one of those Heroes, you know?</i>

351
00:22:00.945 --> 00:22:04.657 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<i>Oh, and you should see him,</i>
<i>he's so cool and really cute!</i>

352
00:22:04.782 --> 00:22:06.617 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<i>He's my new favorite hero on the show!</i>

353
00:22:06.700 --> 00:22:08.118 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
[groaning]

